1514392239224541191.name: Damion Schubert - @ZenOfDesign@Brokentoys.social
1514392239224541191.content: Power Creep is normal in online games because we want players to want to chase and/or buy the new stuff.  But it's a real problem for the crypto community because it means that the old stuff you invested in will probably lose value.

1514392231154696192.name: Damion Schubert - @ZenOfDesign@Brokentoys.social
1514392231154696192.content: You see this all the time in crypto game literature. Remember that laughable mtgDAO pitch a few weeks ago?  One of the things that motivated the team was that... Magic cards can lose value, and this is BAD.
